I think it's just great you do this, everyone involved, especially for free. I don't really expect anything better, and I'm aware, once again, this is a passion project for everyone involved. Bravo and thank you.

It would be cool to maybe capture even more data on the lobbies people faced for those who could be bothered to fill in extra data, maybe for individual umas too, but I appreciate it might only be a very small subset of people who would take the time to reliably fill out the information. I wonder if it's possible to make some sort of overlay app that could track the data directly, a bit like deck/draw tools that work for card games. I appreciate you're doing this for free though, once again. But. You asked.
